Reta y'u [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] yatangije gahunda yo kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere  iyo myuka ikaba iva byumihariko; mu binyabiziga cyane cyane mu modoka hakorwa ubugenzuzi mu binyabiziga byakozwe mbere ya 1992 harebwa amavuta akoresha na za moteri no kugabanya imyuka iva munganda na handi hatandukanye <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/rema-yahagurukiye-ikibazo-cy-imodoka-zisohora-imyuka-ihumanya-ikirere</ref>.

== Intego u Rwanda rufite mu kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere ==
Intego igihugu cy'u [[Rwanda]]  cyihaye yo kugabanya ku gipimo cya 38% imyuka yoherezwa mu kirere ikagipfukirana ibizwi nka (Green House Gases), izaba yagezweho mu gihe cyateganijwe cy'imyaka 10 iri imbere, ibi bikazunganirwa na gahunda zisanzweho zo kubungabunga ibidukikije zashyizweho na leta y'u Rwanda mukubungabunga ibidukikije. Iyi ntego  yo kugabanya 38% ry'imyuka yoherezwa mu kirere izaba yagezweho muri 2030  nkuko Leta y'u Rwanda yabyiemeje <ref>https://umwezi.rw/?p=8960</ref>.

== Ibarurisha mibare ku myuka yorezwa mu kirere mu [[Rwanda]] ==
Bimwe mu byohereza imyuka myinshi mu kirere mu Rwanda hari ibinyabiziga byohereza imyuka ingana na 13%, ibikorwa by'ubwubatsi nk'imihanda n'ibindi byohereza 14% by'imyuka, naho imyuka iva mu butaka ijya mu kirere ingana na 16%, amafumbire mvaruganda yoherezayo mu kirere imyuka ingana na 13%  mu gihe ibishingwe byohereza 5% by'imyuka mu kirere<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/Leta-yizeye-kugabanya-38-yigipimo-cyimyuka-yoherezwa-mu-kirere-mu-myaka-10</ref>.

== Amwe mu masezerano u [[Rwanda]] rwasinye mu kugabanya imyuka yoherezwa mu kirere. ==
Reta y'uRwanda yasinye amwe mu masezerano mpuza mahanga ajyanye no kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere iva mu bikorwa bya muntu aya masezerano naya akurikira :

* Amasezereno ya parisi<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-40117832</ref>
* Amasezerano ya kigali<ref>https://igihe.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/amasezerano-yo-guhagarika-ibyuka-byangiza-ikirere-yagezweho</ref>
* Amasezerano ya Afurika y'iburasirazuba mu kurengera ibidukikije<ref>https://flash.rw/2022/03/02/u-rwanda-rwahawe-miliyari-63-frw-azifashishwa-mu-kurengera-ibidukikije/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=u-rwanda-rwahawe-miliyari-63-frw-azifashishwa-mu-kurengera-ibidukikije</ref>
* Amasezerano ya afurika mu kubungabunga ibidukikije<ref>https://imvahonshya.co.rw/?p=3400</ref>
* Amasezerano mpuzamahanga mu kurengera ibidukikije 
* Nandi atandukanye ajyanye no kurengera ibidukikije hagabanywa imyuka yoherezwa mu kirere <ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/u-rwanda-rwahawe-ikaze-mu-ihuriro-rigamije-kugabanya-imyuka-yangiza-ikirere</ref>.

