Reta y'uRwanda yashyize imbaraga mu kugabanya bimwe mu bikorwa byangiza ibidukikije cyane ibisohora imyuka yangiza ihumanya ikirere .

Murwego rw'ibinyabiziga  hakozwe ibi bikurikira

* Ubugenzuzi bw'ibyotsi bisohaka mu kinyabiziga

* ubukangura mbaga ku binyabiziga bishaje
* Gukimira iyinjizwa ry'ibinyabiziga bishaje mu Rwanda
* Ubukangura mbaga mu gukoresha amavuta  y'ibinyabiziga meza
